                </div>
                <div class="dictentry-bib">
                    <h1><a name="zbk.064.0112a.h0021"></a><a name="h0021"></a>References</h1>
                    <div class="bib" id="zbk.064.0112a.b006">
                        <p class="bib_bib">Fenichel, O. (1945). <i>The Psychoanalytic Theory of
                                Neurosis</i>. New York: Norton.</p>
                    </div>
